summary: [Photo]: Photo of Emiliano Sala’s corpse surfaces online, sparks outrage
title: [Photo]: Photo of Emiliano Sala’s corpse surfaces online, sparks outrage
body:
[Photo]: Photo of Emiliano Sala’s corpse surfaces online, sparks outrage

The internet is abuzz with news following photos of the corpse of footballer Emiliano Sala’s surfacing online.

The photos show the body in a morgue and have since sparked outrage online as many are asking why such an image would be leaked.

The corpse of the 28-year-old Argentinian striker was taken to the Holly Tree Lodge mortuary in Bournemouth, Dorset, hours after it was found on February 6…
